{"tid":817702,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《花木蘭》迪士尼真人版電影已開拍，傳「木須龍」可能回歸！","createTime":"2018-09-13T14:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T19:59:19.000Z","uid":9573,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2091570905d4fa69785b5525863c9fcd42ee4daa","tid":817702,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/82561/5b9954b19b4fc.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F82561%2F5b9954b19b4fc.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=285a4888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/82561/5b9954b1b1031.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F82561%2F5b9954b1b1031.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=8644a618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1998 年上映的迪士尼動畫《花木蘭》是迪士尼第一部以華人故事為主題的動畫電影，也是不少人的童年回憶。而《花木蘭》真人版由女星劉亦菲主演，如今傳出真人版電影中，除了大家耳熟能響的經典配樂會再次出現以外，受歡迎的經典角色「木須龍」也將回歸！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/82561/5b9954b1dce37.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F82561%2F5b9954b1dce37.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=c8b18d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/82561/5b9954b1ce8ff.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F82561%2F5b9954b1ce8ff.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=e091143f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木須龍為花木蘭家中的守護神，被花家祖先派到軍中確保花木蘭的安全，雖然目前木須龍會以什麼形式出現在真人版中仍無法確定，但這角色的回歸，絕對會是《花木蘭》真人版中的一大亮點！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/82561/5b9954b1e3b54.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F82561%2F5b9954b1e3b54.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=ea3585ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了主角劉亦菲以外，甄子丹將飾演女主角的恩師童將軍，李連杰將飾演皇帝，英軍領隊修夫基直言，這兩個入球對拉舒福特十分重要。令人驚喜的是，片中主要的反派角色強大女巫，則將由影后鞏俐出演，卡司陣容可說是非常強大！《花木蘭》真人版預計會在 2020 年 3 月 27 日於北美上映，屆時一定又會掀起一波「花木蘭」風潮！"},{"pid":"fedd7bd963154e0db2a741fb2a7d460edfe4e568","tid":817702,"uid":135313,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"劉亦菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad1bc24f188a6e7a8424f134609bd3128bc3802","tid":817702,"uid":18718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"修夫基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad3a88297fce7737e82055b737d6a858fa0e422","tid":817702,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"M記會唔會重新出四川醬麥樂雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc8c10fba4c4e63f26797895c28e47f17eec4bc","tid":817702,"uid":80443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:24:56.000Z","msg":"哦，乜嗰隻嘢之前畀人割讓咗咩？"},{"pid":"96cc48c05ee1ece6c7bd6aa0b4ed5c8aef951468","tid":817702,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"搵埋黎彼德做賜福就一流"},{"pid":"98794ad22d971edb886140b4054d1cfed32e5f40","tid":817702,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"李連杰唔係有病咩？之前見張相好似就黎死嘅阿伯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91334afd240713df8b28557af89aa4fd88b5bbb0","tid":817702,"uid":9104,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"甄子丹將飾演女主角的恩師童將軍，李連杰將飾演皇帝，英軍領隊修夫基直言，這兩個入球對拉舒福特十分重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8dc23db430f